nl.tno.stormcv.util.connector

Class ClasspathConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tno.stormcv.util.connector.ClasspathConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, FileConnector

    public class ClasspathConnector
extends Object
implements FileConnector
    A FileConnector implementation to read files from the classpath. If a file resides within a jar file it will be copied to the tmp directory before a reference is provided to the caller of the connector. This connector is used for locations starting with classpath://
    Author:
    Corne Versloot
    See Also:
